snippet.textDisplay: I’m also living in JingAn and it’s very interesting to see the in depth video from you.  Are you guys doing ok at Congming Fangcang?  I heard it’s pretty bad… But keep up the good spirit my friend!  Looking forward to seeing more updates from you
